{"tid":1431063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]［警處文件］黑警不拘捕元朗白衫人原因流出！","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:26:26.000Z","uid":258340,"like":682,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f634545fd8f2f29a3c0325d2e404c5e42ee65403","tid":1431063,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9oBB6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9oBB6h.jpg&h=f80207a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/16_jpc/jpc_open_day.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F16_jpc%2Fjpc_open_day.html&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=d35b7c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/16_jpc/jpc_open_day.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">元朗區小朋友細個已經開始<br />\n同daddy mammy 用雷射槍互射作為親子活動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐵通藤條更係元朗區常用教仔工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係你班廢青中老比人打幾下就嗌生嗌死<br />\n仲話點解唔告白衫藏有攻擊性武器、傷人<br />\n<br />\n八鄉警察話 睬你都廢鳩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲只係元朗居民日常交流教仔心得既聯誼活動！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"54b91c4675cccb05947d98a5726ac439a71ec19f","tid":1431063,"uid":258340,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"只有核彈係元朗先至係攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"36420e139d6a8c5278a936c4312fe730930b8ac0","tid":1431063,"uid":258340,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:57:17.000Z","msg":"係你班人少入元朗<br />\n元朗居民用開鐵通打頭 做打招呼"},{"pid":"7411b3a7871a23e57db0024de1c745eaf7b3bad0","tid":1431063,"uid":258340,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"你班廢青中老唔捱得"},{"pid":"37646660bea1db30a3d5337b35